(206, '_transient_wte_messages_8b17f1841b4c89bc41bf4597e988b14b', 'a:10:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:67598;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2021-02-02T18:28:09\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2021-02-02T12:43:09\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=67598\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2021-02-02T18:28:09\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2021-02-02T12:43:09\";s:4:\"slug\";s:66:\"major-update-release-notice-wp-travel-engine-version-4-3-0-is-here\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:108:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/major-update-release-notice-wp-travel-engine-version-4-3-0-is-here/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:70:\"[Major Update Release Notice] WP Travel Engine version 4.3.0 is here !\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:2342:\"<p>Hello, We are excited to announce the release of a major update release for WP Travel Engine.</p>\n<p>In this major update, we have made enhancements to Booking data and payment flow in WP Travel Engine core. We have also optimized the booking process for a more flexible booking with Booking and Payment Notification emails. Furthermore, this version adds support for upcoming features like Multiple checkout and pricing options along with a bunch of enhancements.</p>\n<p><strong>Important Notes</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Email Template</strong> &#8211; We have updated mail tags and added new email templates to support multiple checkouts, payment email notification and to enhance the booking process in this version update, to enable support for multiple bookings, kindly update your email template from Global Settings Screen.</p>\n<p><strong>Booking Screen Updates &#8211;</strong> There are some major changes behind the scenes for saving and obtaining Booking Information in Admin Dashboard, some of the changes include the better display of payment responses and support for Multi-cart options.</p>\n<p>While all of your old bookings will work perfectly without any issues, if you face any issues in the Booking screen after the update, kindly contact our dedicated Support team reporting the issues.</p>\n<p><strong>Enhancements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Enhancement &#8211; Conflict with FontAwesome fixed for Elementor premium addon.</li>\n<li>Enhancement &#8211; New Email Templates added for payment notification and status for Admin and Customers.</li>\n<li>Enhancement &#8211; Preview Email templates right from the settings screen.</li>\n<li>Enhancement &#8211; Optimized booking data to support future Enhancements like Multiple Checkout and Payment processing.</li>\n<li>Fixes &#8211; Minor Bug Fixes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a full description of the changes in this major update release, please check our version <a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/major-update-releasewp-travel-engine-4-3-0/\">release notes here.</a></p>\n<p>If you have any queries regarding the update, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a>. Or, raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine.</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/67598\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=67598\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:62732;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-12-21T21:31:38\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-12-21T15:46:38\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=62732\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-12-21T21:31:38\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-12-21T15:46:38\";s:4:\"slug\";s:64:\"extra-services-new-version-with-multiple-service-options-is-here\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:106:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/extra-services-new-version-with-multiple-service-options-is-here/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:66:\"[Extra Services] New version with multiple service options is here\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:1462:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>Today, we are excited to announce the highly requested feature of the <strong>Extra Services addon &#8211; with multiple service options</strong> is finally here.</p>\n<p>The new update to Extra Services addon lets you add advanced options to your trip extras to extend its functionality even further. We have introduced new service options addition feature that will let your users choose additional options categorized under service. With the enhancements, adding and managing extra services for your trips is now even easier.</p>\n<p><strong>If you are willing to add services like room types and pickup locations for your trips, this update is for you !!</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> We are happy to inform you that the <a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/extra-services-addon-version-2-1-0/\">documentation</a> <strong>has already been updated</strong> to guide you through the Advanced Services Settings. If you are using <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/downloads/extra-services/\">Extra Services</a> with WP Travel Engine we strongly recommend you to update it to the latest version.</p>\n<p>If you have any queries regarding the features or any add-ons, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a>. Or, raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/62732\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=62732\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:56914;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-11-05T13:49:46\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-11-05T08:04:46\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=56914\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-11-05T13:49:46\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-11-05T08:04:46\";s:4:\"slug\";s:68:\"advanced-itinerary-builder-itinerary-elevation-chart-feature-is-here\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:110:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/advanced-itinerary-builder-itinerary-elevation-chart-feature-is-here/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:71:\"[Advanced Itinerary Builder] Itinerary Elevation Chart feature is here.\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:1606:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>Today, we are excited to announce the highly requested feature of the Advanced Itinerary Builder &#8211; <strong>Itinerary Elevation Chart</strong> is finally here.</p>\n<p>Elevation Chart lets you add a detailed elevation profile for the route that your trip itinerary offers. With its easy-to-use settings, it offers your website users a seamless experience in exploring the trekking elevation chart.</p>\n<p>To start using this feature, you will simply need to add &#8220;Location Info&#8221;, with location title and the maximum altitude attained for the day in your itinerary. A beautiful and responsive elevation chart will be automatically generated from the data and displayed above the itineraries toggle on your trip page. The chart is fully customizable with the color of your choice and other visual options.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> We are happy to inform you that the <a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/advanced-itinerary-builder/\">documentation</a> <strong>has already been updated</strong> to guide you through the Elevation Chart Settings. If you are using <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/downloads/advanced-itinerary-builder/\">Advanced Itinerary Builder</a>, we strongly recommend you to update it to the latest version.</p>\n<p>If you have any queries regarding the features or any add-ons, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a>. Or, raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/56914\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=56914\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:41026;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-06-19T18:44:24\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-06-19T12:59:24\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=41026\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-06-19T18:44:24\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-06-19T12:59:24\";s:4:\"slug\";s:51:\"major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-4-0-0-is-here\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:93:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-4-0-0-is-here/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:54:\"[Major Update Release] WP Travel Engine 4.0.0 is here!\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:1420:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>We sent a notification yesterday about the major backend UI update in WP Travel Engine. I am happy to announce that version 4.0.0 has finally rolled out.</p>\n<p>Please <strong>update WP Travel Engine to the latest version</strong> on your website.</p>\n<p><strong>If you face any issues after the 4.0.0 update, we kindly request you to clear the cache from the browser and server.</strong></p>\n<p>As always, if you have any queries regarding the latest update or need help, just send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a> or raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: If you are using any of the WP Travel Engine addons, we strongly recommend you to <strong>update the addons to the latest version</strong> after updating to the WP Travel Engine 4.0.0 to ensure the productivity with the new UI and its features.</p>\n<p>In case if you can not find an update notification for any add-ons, you can also download the purchased theme/add-on from your account on WP Travel Engine. Please go to the below link, and log in using the username and password that was emailed to you from WP Travel Engine.<br />\n<a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/my-account/\">https://wptravelengine.com/my-account/</a></p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/41026\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=41026\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:40720;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-06-17T17:35:00\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-06-17T11:50:00\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=40720\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-06-17T17:35:00\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-06-17T11:50:00\";s:4:\"slug\";s:62:\"major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-4-0-0-is-coming-tomorrow\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:104:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-4-0-0-is-coming-tomorrow/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:65:\"[Major Update Release] WP Travel Engine 4.0.0 is coming tomorrow!\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:1600:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>We are excited to announce that we will be rolling out the major backend UI update with WP Travel Engine 4.0.0 tomorrow i.e. on 18th June 2020.</p>\n<p><b>IMPORTANT NOTE: If you have installed and activated any of the WP Travel Engine Addons, please make sure to update them to the latest available version after updating WP Travel Engine to version 4.0.0.</b></p>\n<p>What’s in there for you?</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Intuitive backend UI</strong></li>\n<li><strong>New Trip Edit Screen</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Updated Booking Screen</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Updated Enquiry Screen</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Updated Settings Screen</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Updated Plugin License Page</strong></li>\n<li><strong>New User Onboarding process</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Features &#8211; </strong>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Default Trip Code</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Cut-Off Time</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Min-Max Participants</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Trip Highlights</strong></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><strong>and more.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can find more details regarding the WP Travel Engine Version 4 update at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-travel-engine-version-4/\">https://wptravelengine.com/wp-travel-engine-version-4/.</a></p>\n<p>As always, if you have any queries regarding the features or any add-ons, just send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a> or raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/40720\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=40720\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:34922;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-03-19T20:06:26\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-03-19T14:21:26\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=34922\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-03-19T20:06:26\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-03-19T14:21:26\";s:4:\"slug\";s:45:\"a-message-to-our-community-regarding-covid-19\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:87:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/a-message-to-our-community-regarding-covid-19/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:45:\"A Message to Our Community Regarding COVID-19\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:3029:\"<p>Hi!</p>\n<p>The global tourism industry has been heavily affected as a result of the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak. We are working to ensure that our customers’ businesses continue to be supported through this difficult time.</p>\n<p>I would like to inform you of some steps we have taken to ensure that our customers can continue to use WP Travel Engine through this crisis.</p>\n<h2>We’d like to help</h2>\n<p>We would like to do our part in supporting our customers to maintain their business through this difficult time. We are taking steps to ensure that travel companies using our products, especially those going through a difficult time, can continue to use them through the financial downtime.</p>\n<h2>Free license renewal</h2>\n<p>With the current unavoidable circumstances due to the COVID-19 outbreak, we recognize that we are facing a global financial drop, especially in the global tourism industry.</p>\n<p>For our part in providing support in these times,  we are offering to renew the customer license of our products to anyone who needs it, for free. This includes our Travel Booking Pro themes and any of our WP Travel Engine addons.</p>\n<p>If your product licenses have expired over the past three months, or since the beginning of 2020, you can get it renewed free of charge.</p>\n<p>Also, considering the possible long-term impact of the COVID-19 crisis, we are also offering an extended 1-year free license to any of our existing customers who need it.</p>\n<p>Just <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">write to us via support ticket</a> and we will renew your license for free.</p>\n<h2>On our side</h2>\n<p>I’d like to assure you that we are closely monitoring the coronavirus situation from our side. We are taking every necessary precaution to ensure that our team remains safe including working remotely.</p>\n<p>We continue to run our operations as usual and do not anticipate any disruption. However, in light of the crisis at hand, our team will be working remotely from the safety of their homes. We will continue to do our best to ensure the same quality in our customer service.</p>\n<p>Nonetheless, considering the extraordinary circumstances, we do hope you will understand any occasional delay.</p>\n<h2>Stay Safe</h2>\n<p>To prevent any chances of being affected by the COVID-19 virus, please take precautionary measures to ensure your safety and that of the people around you.</p>\n<p>There have been many suggestions to prevent contracting the virus, but we believe that washing your hands with soap, maintaining a social distance, and avoiding public gatherings can go a long way towards fighting this crisis.</p>\n<p>We hope that you take the necessary measures as well as aware others of the ways to stay safe in these extraordinary times.</p>\n<p>Make sure you stay safe through this crisis as well, and we will do our best to support our customers from our side. Please let us know if we can help you in any other way.</p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/34922\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=34922\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:30952;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-02-07T21:21:05\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-02-07T15:36:05\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=30952\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-02-07T21:21:05\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-02-07T15:36:05\";s:4:\"slug\";s:80:\"new-payment-gateways-release-say-hello-to-new-addons-payhere-payu-money-checkout\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:122:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/new-payment-gateways-release-say-hello-to-new-addons-payhere-payu-money-checkout/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:91:\"[New Payment Gateways Release] Say Hello to New Addons: PayHere &#038; PayU Money Checkout!\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:3765:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi,</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today, we are excited to announce the release of two new payment gateways &#8211; </span><b>PayHere &amp; PayU Money Checkout.</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> These payment gateways are an extension for the WP Travel Engine that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These payment gateways give your customers a seamless checkout experience through </span><b>a single Online Payment Solution</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You have everything under one roof with these payment gateways.</span></p>\n<p><b>Note</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PayHere accepts the payment from any country as long as you have your business name under Sampath Bank account and supports online payments in the following currencies:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">LKR (Sri Lankan Rupee)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">USD (United States Dollar)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">GBP (Pound Sterling)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">EUR (Euro)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AUD (Australian Dollar)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To know more about it, please visit the </span><b>WP Travel Engine &#8211; </b><a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/downloads/payhere-payment-gateway/\"><b>PayHere Payment Gateway</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayHere-payment-gateway.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30770\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayHere-payment-gateway.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayHere-payment-gateway.jpg 1000w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayHere-payment-gateway-300x205.jpg 300w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayHere-payment-gateway-768x525.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PayU Money Checkout accepts the payment only from India as it supports online payments in Indian Rupee (INR) currency.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To know more about it, please visit the </span><b>WP Travel Engine &#8211; </b><a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/downloads/payu-money-payment-gateway/\"><b>PayU Money Payment Gateway</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayU-payment-gateway.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30813\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayU-payment-gateway.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayU-payment-gateway.jpg 1000w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayU-payment-gateway-300x205.jpg 300w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2020/02/PayU-payment-gateway-768x525.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><br />\nIf you have any queries regarding the features or any add-ons, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a>. Or, raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/30952\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=30952\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:30572;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-02-04T17:48:33\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-02-04T12:03:33\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=30572\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-02-04T17:48:33\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-02-04T12:03:33\";s:4:\"slug\";s:52:\"child-and-infant-price-multi-pricing-feature-is-here\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:94:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/child-and-infant-price-multi-pricing-feature-is-here/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:55:\"[Child and Infant price] Multi-Pricing feature is here.\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:1779:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>Today, we are excited to announce the highly requested feature of the WP Travel Engine &#8211; <strong>a multi-pricing option</strong> is finally here. The feature comes with multiple pricing options from which a tour operator can add different prices for different kinds of people &#8211; adult, child, and infant.</p>\n<p>With the new section “Prices” in this feature, you can add a pricing option label and enable sale options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/multi-pricing.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30576\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/multi-pricing.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"867\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/multi-pricing.png 828w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/multi-pricing-287x300.png 287w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/multi-pricing-768x804.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> We are happy to inform you that this feature <strong>has already been made compatible</strong> with the <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/downloads/trip-fixed-starting-dates/\">Trip Fixed Starting Dates</a> and <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/downloads/group-discount/\">Group Discount</a> add-ons. If you are using these add-ons, we strongly recommend you to update them to the latest version.</p>\n<p>If you have any queries regarding the features or any add-ons, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a>. Or, raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/30572\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=30572\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:28836;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-01-15T17:11:50\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-01-15T11:26:50\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=28836\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-01-15T17:11:50\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-01-15T11:26:50\";s:4:\"slug\";s:53:\"major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-3-0-0-is-here-2\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:95:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-3-0-0-is-here-2/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:54:\"[Major Update Release] WP Travel Engine 3.0.0 is here!\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:2241:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>We sent a notification yesterday about the major update coming to the booking process in WP Travel Engine. I am happy to announce that version 3.0.0 has finally rolled out.</p>\n<p>Please <strong>update WP Travel Engine to the latest version</strong> on your website.</p>\n<p><strong>If you face any issues after the 3.0.0 update, we kindly request you to clear the cache from the browser and server.</strong></p>\n<p>As always, if you have any queries regarding the latest update or need help, just send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a> or raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: If you are using any of the following addons, we strongly recommend you to <strong>update the addons to the minimum required version</strong> before updating to the WP Travel Engine 3.0.0 to ensure the productivity with the new booking process and its features.</p>\n<p><strong>Addons                                                                   Version</strong></p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Group Discount                        1.0.9</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Extra Services                          1.0.2</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; PayPal Express Gateway        1.0.2</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Stripe Payment Gateway         1.0.6</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Trip Fixed Starting Dates         1.2.2</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; PayU Payment Gateway          1.0.4</p>\n<p>YES! We have got your back. If you are not ready to switch to the new improved, conversion-optimized and sales-oriented booking flow updates, we also provide backward compatibility with older versions.</p>\n<p>In case if you update to version 3.0.0 and then want to revert back to the older booking process and checkout flow, please follow this link: <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-travel-engine-3-0-backward-compatibility/\">https://wptravelengine.com/wp-travel-engine-3-0-backward-compatibility/</a></p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n<hr />\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/28836\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=28836\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":16:{s:2:\"id\";i:28629;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-01-14T11:07:16\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-01-14T05:22:16\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:63:\"https://wptravelengine.com/?post_type=wte_messages&#038;p=28629\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2020-01-14T16:25:24\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-01-14T10:40:24\";s:4:\"slug\";s:51:\"major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-3-0-0-is-here\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"wte_messages\";s:4:\"link\";s:93:\"https://wptravelengine.com/release-notes/major-update-release-wp-travel-engine-3-0-0-is-here/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:65:\"[Major Update Release] WP Travel Engine 3.0.0 is coming tomorrow!\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:6823:\"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>After getting multiple requests from you, we are excited to announce that we will be rolling out the major update on the booking process with WP Travel Engine 3.0.0 tomorrow i.e. on 15th January 2020.</p>\n<p>What’s in there for you?</p>\n<p><strong>1. Conversion Optimized Booking Process Indicator</strong></p>\n<p>This new feature allows users to view their booking process progress. It allows users to track how many steps they’ve completed and how much more details are needed to finish their booking process.</p>\n<p>With a booking process indicator, users can visualize how much longer they will need to spend on the website until the booking process is complete.</p>\n<p>Implementing the booking process indicator will help you to create your website well optimized for excellent user experience and also helps to increase conversion rate i.e increase in the volume of bookings.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28651 size-large\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-998x1024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"770\" height=\"790\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-998x1024.png 998w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-292x300.png 292w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-768x788.png 768w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-1496x1536.png 1496w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2. New Booking Form on the Trip Page</strong></p>\n<p>Beautifully designed booking form which helps users to have an optimal booking experience. This booking form is extremely user-friendly and responsive.</p>\n<p>With the new booking form, users can select dates in the calendar, add travelers and select extra services which diminishes the hefty booking process.</p>\n<p data-wp-editing=\"1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28652 size-full\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1.Calendar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"798\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1.Calendar.png 397w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1.Calendar-149x300.png 149w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28653 size-full\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.Travelers.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.Travelers.png 397w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.Travelers-162x300.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28654 size-full\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3.Extra-services.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"736\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3.Extra-services.png 397w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3.Extra-services-162x300.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28655 size-full\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4.Availabe-group-discount-table.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"657\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4.Availabe-group-discount-table.png 397w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4.Availabe-group-discount-table-181x300.png 181w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28656 size-full\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5.View-detail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"911\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5.View-detail.png 397w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5.View-detail-131x300.png 131w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>3. New Checkout Page</strong></p>\n<p>We have redesigned our checkout page and improved the user experience. With the new checkout page, we have removed unneeded steps and unnecessary form fields making the booking process fast and efficient.</p>\n<p>We have also placed the booking summary information on the right side of the checkout page.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28651 size-large\" src=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-998x1024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"770\" height=\"790\" srcset=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-998x1024.png 998w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-292x300.png 292w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-768x788.png 768w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page-1496x1536.png 1496w, https://wptravelengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6.Checkout-page.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: If you are using any of the following addons, we strongly recommend you to <strong>update the addons to the minimum required version</strong> before updating to the WP Travel Engine 3.0.0 to ensure the productivity with the new booking process and its features.</p>\n<p><strong>Addons                                                                   Version</strong></p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Group Discount                        1.0.9</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Extra Services                          1.0.2</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; PayPal Express Gateway        1.0.2</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Stripe Payment Gateway         1.0.6</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; Trip Fixed Starting Dates         1.2.2</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine &#8211; PayU Payment Gateway          1.0.4</p>\n<p>YES! We have got your back. If you are not ready to switch to the new improved, conversion-optimized and sales-oriented booking flow updates, we also provide backward compatibility with older versions.</p>\n<p>In case if you update to version 3.0.0 and then want to revert back to the older booking process and checkout flow, please follow this link: <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-travel-engine-3-0-backward-compatibility/\">https://wptravelengine.com/wp-travel-engine-3-0-backward-compatibility/</a></p>\n<p>As always, if you have any queries regarding the features or any add-ons, just send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:support@wptravelengine.com\">support@wptravelengine.com</a> or raise a ticket at <a href=\"https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/\">https://wptravelengine.com/support-ticket/.</a></p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>WP Travel Engine Team</p>\n<hr />\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages/28629\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:53:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/wte_messages\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/types/wte_messages\";}}s:13:\"wp:attachment\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:4:\"href\";s:59:\"https://wptravelengine.com/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=28629\";}}s:6:\"curies\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:4:\"name\";s:2:\"wp\";s:4:\"href\";s:23:\"https://api.w.org/{rel}\";s:9:\"templated\";b:1;}}}}}', 'no'),
