(216, '_transient_wp_travel_engine_store_addons_list', '{\n    \"products\": [\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 44702,\n                \"slug\": \"zapier\",\n                \"title\": \"Zapier\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-07-17 16:19:24\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 11:10:29\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=44702\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Zapier is an addon for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that lets users create Zapier automation ( through catch webhooks ) for booking and enquiries data. With the addon, you can get all of your booking and enquiries data to multiple webhooks created in the Zapier application.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the addon, users will be able to simply integrate their bookings and enquiries data from WP Travel Engine to their Zapier account that opens up possibilities with 400+ third party web services integration available in Zapier, including Highrise, Twilio, Campaign Monitor, MailChimp, Xero, Zendesk, Dropbox, Google Docs and more.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2>Requirements<\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Requirements for the WP Travel Engine - Zapier addon are:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine - v.4.0.6 or later<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A Zapier account<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>Minimal configuration<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Zapier addon takes minimal configuration or setups. You can simply activate the plugin, set up your desired webhooks for bookings and enquiries data, and everything else is automatically handled by the webhook, every time a new booking or enquiry is created on your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Multiple webhooks support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Zapier addon supports the addition of multiple webhooks from Zapier zaps for booking and enquiries. You can add a set of webhooks for booking and enquiries for your integration setups on Zapier and all of the added webhooks will be triggered when booking or enquiry is created. This will give you an additional level of flexibility to manage and automate your tasks with Zapier.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Webhooks integration testing<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Testing a webhook after addition in WP Travel Engine is easy with Zapier addon. After adding a webhook name and URL, you can use the button beside to trigger the webhook with sample booking or enquiry data. This feature will let you configure and map fields to specific headings\\/lists and prepare your configurations so that you can automate the task next time you receive a booking or enquiry request on your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Automate webhooks trigger for booking\\/enquiry<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Zapier addon has an easy checkbox toggle that lets you enable or disable automation of webhooks triggers. Enable or disable the automation for your booking and enquiry webhooks trigger as per your requirements.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Manual Zapier webhook trigger support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Want your old bookings and enquiries to be added support for webhooks? After setting up the webhooks for bookings and enquiries, you can choose the bookings\\/enquiries from the list that you would like to send to the webhook trigger and the booking\\/enquiries will be sent to the booking and enquiries webhooks defined in settings.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<i><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Note: As the webhooks trigger sends a PHP cURL request to Zapier\\u2019s webhooks, please make sure your PHP cURL settings are enabled on your web server. Also, bulk manual webhook triggers should also be used cautiously( not many bookings\\/enquiries at a time ) as multiple cURLs might lead to server request timeout.<\\/span><\\/i>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Continued development and excellent support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request, or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2>Screenshots<\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Screenshot.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-44711 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Screenshot-1024x369.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"277\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/zapier.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-44713 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/zapier-1024x383.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"288\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/screenshsaot.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-44715 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/screenshsaot-1024x289.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"217\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/s.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-44716 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/s-1024x194.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"146\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Zapier lets users create Zapier automation ( through catch webhooks ) for booking and enquiries data.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/zapier-integretion.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 30074,\n                \"slug\": \"currency-converter\",\n                \"title\": \"Currency Converter\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-07-03 16:38:46\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 11:13:29\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=30074\",\n                \"content\": \"Currency Converter is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that lets you convert the trip price between multiple currencies. You can add multiple currencies of your choice and let your customers have an <span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">easy conversion of currencies and display<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> of prices.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\nWith the addon, you can also enable the geo-locate feature to automatically detect your users\' location and display the trip price in relevant currency.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn addition, the currency converter switcher can also be displayed in the booking calendar giving extra flexibility for customers to switch between the trip price in different currencies.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou can also display the currency converter switcher via Widget and Shortcode.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Note: <\\/strong>Currency Converter lets you convert trip price between multiple currencies, however, the trip booking and payment can only be processed through the admin defined currency.\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Feature Highlights<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Easy to use<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You just have to list which currency support you would like to add and you are good to go. You can directly add the currency converter at the top of the booking calendar on the trip page by controlling a single checkbox.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Widget Support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also add a widget to display the currency converter option from the widgets section.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Shortcode Support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also add the shortcode [ wte_currency_converter ] to display the currency converter option from the editor or on the PHP template.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Automatic Currency Converter<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can set the currency converter API to enable the Auto-update of the currency and convert one currency to another easily.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Geo Locate<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also geolocate the visitor to display the currency as per the location.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Sticky Currency Converter floating bar<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also enable the floating currency converter menu bar on the right to ease users in switching between currencies.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4>Screenshots<\\/h4>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-urrency-converter-backend.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42898\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-urrency-converter-backend.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1134\\\" height=\\\"1536\\\" \\/><\\/a> <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-urrency-converter-floating.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42899\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-urrency-converter-floating.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1363\\\" height=\\\"586\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Currency Converter lets users display and compare trip prices in available currencies or Geolocate.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Currency-Converter.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.4\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 42678,\n                \"slug\": \"coupon-code\",\n                \"title\": \"Coupon Code\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-07-02 19:29:23\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 11:35:52\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=42678\",\n                \"content\": \"Do you occasionally run discount offers for trip bookings on special occasions like Black Friday, Christmas, New Year? Providing your customers with Coupon Codes will attract your travelers and in turn, increase your sales.\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Coupon Code is an extension for\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> to generate a quick form to let site visitors use the coupon discount during the trip checkout.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This easy, on-the-go, <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">one-stop travel companion addon helps you<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> easily manage discount campaigns through either flat discount or percentage discount.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Feature Highlights<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Easy to use<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You just have to create the coupon from the admin and set its name, valid start date, valid expiry date and you are good to go. No need to set other settings at all and you can immediately start to use the coupon.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Unlimited Coupons<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You are free to create unlimited coupons as per required.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Start And Expiry Date<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can simply set the start and end date for the coupon and it will only be valid during that time period.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Number of Use Control<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can set the count of the coupon to limit how many times the coupon will be used. For e.g. If you set the number of uses of the coupon to 100, the coupon can only be used by any user to 100 times regardless of when or who has used the coupon.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Trip Specific Restriction<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also restrict where the coupon will be used. You can restrict the coupon to be used only on a particular trip if required.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Discount Type<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can either set the discount type to a flat amount or set it on a percentage to let the add-on calculate the discount amount accordingly.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4>Screenshots<\\/h4>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/landing-page-coupon.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42717\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/landing-page-coupon.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1365\\\" height=\\\"777\\\" \\/><\\/a><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42715\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-coupons-tab-general.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"909\\\" height=\\\"1157\\\" \\/><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42714\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-coupons-tab-restriction.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"883\\\" height=\\\"581\\\" \\/>\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-coupon-front.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42716\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-coupon-front.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"793\\\" height=\\\"819\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Coupon Code helps you to easily manage discount campaigns through either flat discount or percentage discount.\\u00a0\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Coupon-code.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.5\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 40085,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-code\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Code\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-06-18 18:21:18\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 11:34:11\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=40085\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Code is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that lets you define your own custom Trip Code. The add-on lets you add unique trip code to your trips that can be used as an identifier to manage trips, availability, bookings, and inventory SKU.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the addon, you can edit the default Trip Code defined in WP Travel Engine to customize as per your travel business requirements and display it anywhere in the posts\\/pages\\/tabs and widget using the shortcode.\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">In addition, the custom-defined Trip Code is displayed in checkout mini-cart, booking emails, and thank you page giving extra details about the trip to the customers.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Code addon also extends the SKU defined for the Trip in Review Rich Snippets.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4>Screenshots<\\/h4>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/trip-code-edit.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-40373\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/trip-code-edit.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1281\\\" height=\\\"469\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/checkout-trip-code.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-40375\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/checkout-trip-code.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1600\\\" height=\\\"804\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/booking-trip-code-1.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-40380\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/booking-trip-code-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1282\\\" height=\\\"637\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Code is an extension for WP Travel Engine that lets you define your own custom Trip Code. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/Trip-code.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"19.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"49.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"69.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 37061,\n                \"slug\": \"itinerary-downloader\",\n                \"title\": \"Itinerary Downloader\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-04-23 16:45:08\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:06:30\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=37061\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine - Itinerary Downloader is an extension for the WP Travel Engine plugin to generate the itinerary PDF and include various content of the trip to create an offline, quick accessible trip detail brochure file to help you get updated and plan every moment of your trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It\'s easy to get quick detail about the trip without constantly reaching the site online. <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon grants the ability to download the trip details including various sections such as trip overview, trip availability, trip cost, trip itinerary, trip fact, most frequently asked question about trip, quick contact detail, and so on.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Once the PDF generated is downloaded, these PDF itineraries can even quickly be accessed on the phone, so even when the internet isn\\u2019t available, everything can still go according to plan.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This one-stop travel companion addon helps you access the important most necessary details about the trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Feature Highlights<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Itinerary Download Button<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can directly add the shortcode into any of the trip pages and it will generate the quick link to generate the pdf on a single click.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Send Itinerary to Email<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also change the setting to create the popup form for the itinerary downloader. When added to the email, it will generate the pdf file and send the pdf to the user email as an attachment.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Ease of use<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Easy to use and through shortcode, an easy shortcode is available to create buttons to download the itinerary. A click will automatically pull data and download and send the pdf to email as required.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Mailchimp Integration<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When email popup form enabled and MailChimp API key added and after configuring the few other settings, you can also expand your subscription while sending the user itinerary pdf. This is easily configurable through various settings.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Configuration Settings<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This addon offers great flexibility of configuration. You can configure the text to be displayed, to include\\/hide particular sections and other smaller configurable settings to control various aspects of the pdf file generation.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Continuous Development &amp; Support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request, or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>User Consent Settings<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can configure the user consent option to get user consent or control the MailChimp integration. If enabled and made required, the user will be forced to provide consent in order to send <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Pdf to email. Or you can also give users the option to be included for a subscription list or not accordingly. Important and useful for GDPR reasons.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Screenshots<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Itinerary-downloader-5-1-pdf-content-setting.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43776\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Itinerary-downloader-5-1-pdf-content-setting.png\\\" alt=\\\"Itinerary Downloader - Setting\\\" width=\\\"1181\\\" height=\\\"1433\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Itinerary-downloader-5-2-pdf-content-setting.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43777\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Itinerary-downloader-5-2-pdf-content-setting.png\\\" alt=\\\"Itinerary Downloader - Setting\\\" width=\\\"1189\\\" height=\\\"1653\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/04\\/wte-itinerary-downloader-front-button.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-37233\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/04\\/wte-itinerary-downloader-front-button.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"809\\\" height=\\\"194\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/04\\/wte-itinerary-downloader-front-email-form.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-37234\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/04\\/wte-itinerary-downloader-front-email-form.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"876\\\" height=\\\"523\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Itinerary Downloader is an extension for the WP Travel Engine plugin to generate the itinerary PDF and include various content of the trip to create an offline, quick accessible trip detail brochure file.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/04\\/Itinerary-Downloader.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.3\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 34335,\n                \"slug\": \"file-downloads\",\n                \"title\": \"File Downloads\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-03-12 12:09:12\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:05:24\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=34335\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine - File Downloads is an extension for the WP Travel Engine plugin to add physical downloadable files to the trip detail page. This allows you to list various important files on your trip detail page such as digital brochures, info on Government rules &amp; policies, the company brochure, immediate notice to travelers, offline maps and guides, public transport information, airport information, informative handbooks on language or local dialect, high-quality photos and so on.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon grants the ability to upload such files and manage it either globally or through a specific trip to list the various files for the user to either view or save offline.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This addon adds transparency and clarity of the information to the user. This addon is also very handy to Tour Operators for conveying required info to users prior to or during the travel.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Feature Highlights<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Unlimited Number Of Files<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can easily add an unlimited number of files. There is virtually no limit on how many files can be added or managed per the trip requirement.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Ease in use<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Since the files can be added through the default WordPress Media Library, it is simple to find files, upload, and manage them.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Shortcodes<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Shortcode is available to list the files anywhere on the site as per your requirement.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>File Types<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Supports file types Pdf, Doc, Docx, as well as images and text files to match your requirement.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Sortable\\u00a0<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can sort and arrange the files in a custom order and save it as per your need.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Configurations Settings<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This addon offers great flexibility of configuration. You can list the globally uploaded files along with the trip specific uploaded files, force list global files along with trip specific files, add instant download (on one click), and more...<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Continuous Development &amp; Support<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request, or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Minor Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Multi-select upload<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can select multiple files at one time for an upload avoiding a major hassle.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><strong>Rename uploaded files<\\/strong>\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The plugin allows you to rename uploaded files in the File Uploader. This way, you won\\u2019t have to re-upload misnamed files.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Quick Preview<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can get a quick preview of the files you have uploaded in the browser for file types such as images, text files, and pdf files.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Replace files in one click<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You don\\u2019t have to worry if you upload the wrong file by mistake, as you can easily replace it with the correct file with just a click.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Avoid repeated files<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can avoid repeating the same files from the global and trip specific files list as the plugin automatically omits repeated files.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Selectively add global files<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The add\\/edit page features an Add Global File option which allows you to selectively add global files which can vary according to the situation.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2>Screenshots<\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-file-downloads-global-setting-1.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43759\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-file-downloads-global-setting-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1207\\\" height=\\\"1123\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-file-downloads-global-setting-2.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43760\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-file-downloads-global-setting-2.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1183\\\" height=\\\"1013\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-file-downloads-trip.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43761\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-file-downloads-trip.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"873\\\" height=\\\"1465\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/wte-file-downloads-trip-front.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-34397\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/wte-file-downloads-trip-front.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"814\\\" height=\\\"624\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"File Downloads is a custom addon for WP Travel Engine plugin that helps you add downloadable files to the trip individual post.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/file-downloads.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.3\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 33247,\n                \"slug\": \"form-editor\",\n                \"title\": \"Form Editor\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-03-02 17:29:29\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:09:17\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=33247\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Form Editor is a premium add-on to WP Travel Engine plugin that lets you customize the forms in the WP Travel Engine core plugin. With the addon, you can add, edit, remove and easily sort the form fields used in WP Travel Engine. The addon provides flexible options to manipulate Trip Enquiry Form, Booking Form, Traveller\\u2019s Information Form, and Emergency Contact Form all from one central options page right in your Admin Dashboard.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The form editor addon provides an ultimate solution to the travel business owners to create and modify forms as per their business-specific needs and get the most out of website visitors. With the addon, creating user-friendly forms for all the enquiry, booking and checkout process is super easy and flexible.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With intuitive UI, easy interface and tons of options for customization, you can now take full control of the WP Travel Engine forms on your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Features of Form Editor Addon<\\/b>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Add form fields<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The Form Editor addon lets you add your custom fields under a wide range of field types available within the plugin. You can now collect additional information from your travellers through the built-in form in WP Travel Engine by simply adding fields of your choice.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/Screenshot-5.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-33258\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/Screenshot-5.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"548\\\" height=\\\"824\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Edit form fields<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The Form Editor addon lets you edit the existing form fields in all of the forms easily. You can now edit labels, add classes or reorder the placement of form fields as per your choice or requirements.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/Screenshot-6.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-33259\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/Screenshot-6.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1432\\\" height=\\\"577\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Form fields sorting<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Sorting field in each of the forms is now easy with simple drag &amp; drop. Form editor add-on makes it easy to sort all of the fields in WP Travel Engine as per your requirements. The sorting of fields is applicable for both default fields and newly added fields and takes customization of forms to the next level.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/Peek-2020-03-02-13-51.gif\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-33260\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/Peek-2020-03-02-13-51.gif\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1080\\\" height=\\\"471\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Deleting form fields<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Form Editor also lets you delete any unwanted fields ( Except for required ones ) in any of the forms easily with a single click in the back-end user interface.<\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Reset fields<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Messed up form fields while editing or want to get back the default fields that were accidentally deleted? Simply press on the \\u201cReset to defaults\\u201d button to reset the changes and get back the old fields.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.\\u00a0<\\/span>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Form Editor is a premium add-on to WP Travel Engine plugin that lets you customize the forms in the WP Travel Engine core plugin.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/03\\/form-editor.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.2\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 31567,\n                \"slug\": \"advanced-itinerary-builder\",\n                \"title\": \"Advanced Itinerary Builder\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-02-17 14:07:53\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:10:22\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=31567\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Advanced Itinerary Builder is an extension for the WP Travel Engine plugin to add informative and descriptive details per day in the Itinerary section of a particular trip. With the addon, you can showcase your trip\\u2019s details in a much more interactive approach.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon features advanced itinerary content which enables the use of the rich-text editor, attractive gallery, day-by-day information, details per destination, accommodation, activities and other features that will make your trip packages look more beautiful and informative for your customers.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This addon adds transparency and clarity of activities for each day on a particular trip to your visitors on a whole different level. Tour operators can promote their trips with the maximum amount of information for each day throughout the trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Feature Highlights<\\/b>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Rich text editor for itinerary description<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Advanced Itinerary Builder provides the WYSIWYG editor to add your itinerary descriptions. This means that you will have the flexibility to add images, videos, formatted texts, and rich-content to describe the itinerary details for each of the days.<\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Itinerary images gallery<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon provides an additional images gallery upload section where you can showcase all the images you want to describe the activities for the day. The images will be displayed in a responsive popup gallery in the front-end right below the description content. You can add multiple images that will be shown in the scrollable section.<\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Itinerary duration information<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Advanced itinerary Builder also provides you with an additional duration field that lets you display duration of activities for the day in optional hours and minutes units. This adds additional flexibility to your itineraries making them flexible and easy to plan.<\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Meals included information\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Another crucial itinerary detail that lets your users get a clear hit of meals included during the day of the itinerary. The easy UI and concise options will let you easily provide information about the meals included within the day for the trip package.<\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><b>Sleeping Mode<\\/b><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Sleeping mode information field lets you add unique sleeping modes your trip offers for each itinerary day through flexible selection options. You can add custom sleeping mode options as per your requirements from global settings and choose the mode for each individual day.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The sleeping mode information also comes with a rich-text editor that helps you display information with images\\/videos and formatted content about the sleeping mode\\/accommodation options available throughout your package. The information is displayed in yet another responsive popup with description content.<\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li id=\\\"8-toc-title\\\" class=\\\"betterdocs-content-heading\\\"><strong>Itinerary Elevation Chart<\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nElevation Chart lets you add a detailed elevation profile for the route that your trip itinerary offers. With its easy-to-use settings, it offers your website users a seamless experience in exploring the trekking elevation chart.\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine - Advanced Itinerary Builder is a complete package that lets you display descriptive information about your itinerary days in each trip package. With the features and flexibility, you can showcase your trip itinerary highlights to your customers easily.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-advanced-itinerary-trip-setting-1.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43736\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-advanced-itinerary-trip-setting-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"872\\\" height=\\\"883\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/11\\/AI-Fields-Details-1.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-56827\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/11\\/AI-Fields-Details-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1038\\\" height=\\\"1503\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/11\\/AI-Elevation-Chart.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-56829\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/11\\/AI-Elevation-Chart.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1000\\\" height=\\\"592\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/iti-display.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-31817\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/iti-display.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"778\\\" height=\\\"670\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/iti-popup.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-31818\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/iti-popup.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1018\\\" height=\\\"681\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Advanced Itinerary Builder is an extension for the WP Travel Engine plugin to add informative and descriptive details per day in the Itinerary section of a particular trip.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/Advanced-itinerary-builder.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.7\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 31412,\n                \"slug\": \"midtrans-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"Midtrans Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-02-13 11:35:19\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:13:20\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=31412\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Midtrans Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments via <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/midtrans.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Midtrans<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, one of Indonesia\\u2019s popular merchant services.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the Midtrans booking system for trip booking by setting up Midtrans Account with key details \\u2013 Merchant ID, Client Key, and Server Key.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via Midtrans Payment Gateway, they are redirected to your merchant account on Midtrans where they are requested to make the payment. Midtrans handles the payments and redirects the traveler back to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which payment modes does Midtrans currently support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Midtrans Payment Gateway supports the payment modes such as Credit Card, Debit Card, Bank Transfer, e-wallet, and Over the Counter payments.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/midtrans.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Midtrans official page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Note: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Midtrans Payment Gateway works only in Indonesia with Indonesian Rupiah (IDR) currency.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/02\\/Midtrans-urls.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-31537\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/02\\/Midtrans-urls.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"832\\\" height=\\\"399\\\" \\/><\\/a> <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/02\\/midtrans-settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-31541\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/02\\/midtrans-settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"817\\\" height=\\\"855\\\" \\/><\\/a> <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/02\\/midtrans-payment-modes.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-31543\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/02\\/midtrans-payment-modes.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"389\\\" height=\\\"590\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Midtrans Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments via Midtrans, one of Indonesia\\u2019s popular merchant services.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/midtrans-payment-gateway.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"IDR\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 30752,\n                \"slug\": \"payu-money-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayU Money Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-02-06 17:48:46\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:15:25\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=30752\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Payment Gateway is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows you to accept trips and tour payments via one of the leading financial services from India, PayU Money.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayU Money Payment Gateway for trip booking by setting up PayU Money Account with key details - <\\/span><b>Merchant Key and Merchant Salt.<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayU Money Payment Gateway, the payment page opens as a pop-up on your website which is a completely redirection less payment experience.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This payment gateway gives your customers a seamless checkout experience that keeps them in the framework of your website throughout the booking process and enables them to use their Credit\\/Debit card to pay without sharing any sensitive information.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Payment Gateway supports the payment modes such as Credit Card, Debit Card and only accepts payment in Indian Rupee (INR) currency. To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/developer.payumoney.com\\/bolt-checkout\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Checkout page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Note: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Payment Gateway works only in India with Indian Rupee (INR) currency.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"30815,30816\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayU Money Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trips and tour payments via one of the leading financial services from India, PayU Money.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayU-payment-gateway.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"INR\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 30754,\n                \"slug\": \"payhere-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayHere Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-02-06 15:49:00\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:16:10\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=30754\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere Payment Gateway is an extension for the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments via one of Sri Lanka\\u2019s popular merchant services, PayHere.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayHere booking system for trip booking by setting up PayHere Account with key details \\u2013 <strong>Payment Merchant ID and PayHere Merchant Secret<\\/strong>.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayHere Payment Gateway, they are redirected to your merchant account on PayHere where they are requested to login and make the payment. PayHere handles the payments and redirects the traveler back to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which countries does PayHere support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere is a payment processing service for any businesses to conveniently accept online payments locally or globally from customers all around the world. It connects local and international buyers and sellers on a single platform with multiple ways to pay.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere allows you to accept all local and global payment methods available in Sri Lanka through a single Online Payment Solution. You have everything under one roof with this payment gateway.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Payment from any country can be accepted, as long as you have a Sampath account under your business and use LKR, USD, GBP, EUR, and AUD as the transaction currency. To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.payhere.lk\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere Global Page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayHere-Settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30771\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayHere-Settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"980\\\" height=\\\"833\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"30772,30773\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayHere Payment Gateway is an extension for the WP Travel Engine that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments via one of Sri Lanka\\u2019s popular merchant services, PayHere.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayHere-payment-gateway.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"AUD\",\n                    \"EUR\",\n                    \"GBP\",\n                    \"LKR\",\n                    \"USD\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 22896,\n                \"slug\": \"trips-embedder\",\n                \"title\": \"Trips Embedder\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-11-07 08:33:04\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:20:53\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=22896\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder is an addon for WP Travel Engine that lets you quickly add\\/embed selected trips in between your blog posts and website pages content area, right from the WordPress WYSIWYG content editor.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the addon, you can easily display the details of your trip in grid or list format right in between posts or page contents, giving your readers easier access to related trip details.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon adds an additional button to your posts and page content editor, that pops open an easy UI to choose and display your desired trips.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Trips-Embedder-button.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22921\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Trips-Embedder-button.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1094\\\" height=\\\"325\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Popup.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22945\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Popup.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1323\\\" height=\\\"862\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The embedded trips are then shown right in-between your posts\\/page content to the visitors. Visitors can easily view the trips in the grid ( with carousel ) or list layout and access to get more details of the trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Grid Layout<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/grid.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22925\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/grid.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"985\\\" height=\\\"559\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>List Layout<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/list.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22926\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/list.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"973\\\" height=\\\"496\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon also introduces <\\/span><b>new exciting Gutenberg Blocks<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> for WP Travel Engine plugin. You can now insert your trips in a list or grid with ease even with the new WordPress Gutenberg Editor.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery size=\\\"full\\\" columns=\\\"2\\\" link=\\\"none\\\" ids=\\\"22930,22933\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Blogs and information pages play a vital role in Travel and Tour company business as they are the gateway for potential travelers seeking information\\/suggestions through your website. Blog articles are also a good source of information that potential travelers seek out.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon lets you easily embed your trips in your blog articles and pages. Having the list of your recommended trips in a concise list or grid layout lets the readers have a glance at related trips right while reading the content and helps in better conversion towards the trips.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Addon Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Simple and effective UI<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon is simple to install and use with no additional configurations required. After installing and activating the addon, new content editor button and Gutenberg Blocks are available to use and embed your trips to new and old blog posts and pages easily as per your requirements.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Embedder layout options<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon provides two different layouts to display your selected trips. A grid layout, with a carousel and list layout, can be chosen as per your requirements. Both layouts are concise and effective to show maximum information about trips chosen to display.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/layout.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22940\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/layout.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"918\\\" height=\\\"524\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Number of posts options<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon provides lets you decide how many trips to display in a single embed with an easy user interface. You can also choose no. of trips to display from your desired destinations, activities or trip type.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/postsnumber.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23036\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/postsnumber.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"703\\\" height=\\\"652\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Gutenberg Blocks<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Two different Gutenberg blocks are added in the Trips embedder addon that adds extra flexibility for the users using new WordPress Gutenberg Editor for posts and page content creation. New blocks take advantage of the powerful ReactJS based UI for seamless usability with WordPress Gutenberg blocks.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">External Embeds<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It\\u2019s super easy to embed trips from your site into your or your affiliate\\u2019s external website. To embed trips into any page, place the given HTML into the content area. Trips Embedder will automatically generate an Iframe and display your selected trips in the front end. The external website should not necessarily have WordPress installation or WP Travel Engine and its add-ons installed.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/12\\/trips-embedder.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-25664\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/12\\/trips-embedder.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"945\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.<\\/span>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trips Embedder lets you quickly add\\/embed selected trips in between your blog posts and website pages content area, right from the WordPress WYSIWYG content editor. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/trips-embedder-banner.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.3\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20573,\n                \"slug\": \"extra-services\",\n                \"title\": \"Extra Services\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-10-22 08:08:01\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:22:12\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20573\",\n                \"content\": \"<strong>Extra Services Addon version 2.0.4 with major enhancements released !! To know more about the new features in the latest updates please check the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.wptravelengine.com\\/docs\\/extra-services-addon-version-2-1-0\\/\\\">feature update documentation here<\\/a><\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Extra Services is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> to add <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">additional services for trips<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. The add-on makes it easier for the tour operators to add <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">services like airport pick-up, hotel drop-off, vehicle rental, or any other services you want to the trips.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The tour operators and travel agencies can specify the extra services and their rates while creating the package. Later, travelers can book the package along with extra services at a specified additional cost.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Extra Services can be both created globally or applied to each trip individually.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can add a service title, description, and price that the traveler can select on per traveler or on a per unit basis.\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/advanced-pricing.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-62728 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/advanced-pricing.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1386\\\" height=\\\"874\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-62729 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/selected.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1172\\\" height=\\\"417\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/fe.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-62727 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/fe.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"454\\\" height=\\\"785\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Extra Services makes it easier for the tour operators to add services like airport pick-up, hotel drop-off, vehicle rental, or any other services you want to the trips.\\u00a0\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.6\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20468,\n                \"slug\": \"user-history\",\n                \"title\": \"User History\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-09-27 07:26:07\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:24:37\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20468\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">User History is a simple and effective addon that lets WP Travel Engine plugin users track and store browsing history of customers before bookings and enquiries are sent. With the lightweight addon, site admins can track the exact path and pages customers visited before actually making booking or enquiry.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The add-on gives you the desired insights on how customers are visiting your website, information on the referral link and the exact path followed before actually making booking and enquiry request. When a booking or enquiry is made from your website, you can view a piece of additional information regarding the customer browsing history along with the booking\\/enquiry details.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43478\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1287\\\" height=\\\"853\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As a travel\\/tour operator or agency it is very important to get the information on how customers are visiting your website. The information is very helpful to learn about the overall site\\u2019s browsing information. Site admins can easily see and analyze the information to get better conversion rates for bookings and enquiries.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Along with the details on URLs visited, the addon also gathers and displays information on how long the customer visited each page before making the request.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Addon Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Simple and effective<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon is simple to install and use with minimal configurations required. You just need to install and activate the plugin on your site, the rest of the work will be handled by the addon automatically. Without any additional configurations, start getting the browsing history information on the site admin dashboard for every booking and enquiry requests made afterward.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get time elapsed information<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get automatically calculated time duration for each page visited by users, also the information on total timespan customer stayed on your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking-time.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43482\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking-time.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1287\\\" height=\\\"853\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Referral link information<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get information about your site\\u2019s traffic. With WP Travel Engine user history addon, you can easily view the information of the referral link from where customers visited your site. The details will help you in analytics and preparing marketing strategies for your travel business.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get user history in booking emails<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the new {user_history} email tag, you can now choose to get the user history details in your booking email notification also. See all of the browsing history details from the customers right in the booking notification email on the go.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-email.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43484\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-email.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"678\\\" height=\\\"825\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Cookie consent information<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine user history addon also provides additional cookie consent information which site admins can easily enable, configure and edit. As user history tracking depends on the use of cookies, you can easily inform your customers about your cookie policies.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-20527 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/cookie-consent.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"402\\\" height=\\\"216\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Gravity forms support<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine user history addon extends support with Gravity Forms, one of the most popular forms plugin in WordPress. With the support site admins can get all the information and benefits of user history addon even while using Gravity forms form for booking\\/enquiries right in the entry details screen.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/GF-Support.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20547 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/GF-Support.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1589\\\" height=\\\"846\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can choose individually each of the gravity forms in your site you want to track and save user history information.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you are using Gravity Forms plugin on your website, Gravity forms selection settings for user history are available in <\\/span><b>Admin Dashboard &gt; WP Travel Engine &gt; Settings &gt; Extensions &gt; User History &gt; Gravity form(s) to capture user history<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Select-GF.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20560 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Select-GF.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1347\\\" height=\\\"525\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request, or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update. <\\/span>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"WP Travel Engine user history addon is a simple and effective addon that lets WP Travel Engine plugin users track and store browsing history of customers before bookings and enquiries are sent.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/user-story.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20311,\n                \"slug\": \"himalayan-bank-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-09-24 09:02:06\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:25:32\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20311\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of the leading banks in Nepal, Himalayan Bank.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies in Nepal can enable the Himalayan Bank Payment gateway for trip booking by setting up Himalayan Account with key details \\u2013 <\\/span><b>Merchant ID<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and <\\/span><b>Secret Key<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway, the traveler is taken to Himalayan Bank to make a secure payment. After payment, the trip booking is confirmed and the traveler is redirected to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">For redirection, you should ask Himalayan Bank to set the <\\/span><b>Backend-URL<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and <\\/span><b>Frontend-URL<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> of your site on their server. Backend-URL is the URL where you get the response of your payment from the server and the Frontend-URL is the URL where the payer is redirected after successful payment is made.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway incorporates Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Union Pay cards and accepts payment in Nepali(NPR) and US currency. This results in increased conversion rates, improved customer experience and access to the global market.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Note:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway works in Nepal with Nepali and US currency only.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway works on the WordPress site and ONLY with <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel\\u00a0 Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> plugin.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"20312,20316,20313\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of the leading banks in Nepal, Himalayan Bank.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/himalayan-payment-gateway-1000x683.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"49.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"NPR\",\n                    \"USD\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 7093,\n                \"slug\": \"paypal-express-checkout-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayPal Express Checkout Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-12-28 08:19:51\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:26:44\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=7093\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayPal Express Checkout Payment Gateway is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments through PayPal Express. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayPal Express Checkout system for trip booking by setting up PayPal Express Account with key details - <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Client ID <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">and <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayPal Secret<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler is ready to checkout with their PayPal account, they simply have to click the PayPal Checkout button which will redirect them to a PayPal checkout page. All billing and customer details are completed on the PayPal Express checkout page before the traveler is redirected back to your travel website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which countries does PayPal Express support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayPal Express is available in most countries. <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">To know if your country is supported, please see the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">complete <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/developer.paypal.com\\/docs\\/classic\\/api\\/country_codes\\/#countries-supported-in-paypal-payments\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">list here<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Do PayPal Express require my site to have an SSL certificate?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">An SSL certificate is not 