heir website. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews extension adds a Trip Reviews sub-menu and a Review Tab on activation. Travel agency or tour operators (admins) can add reviews from both the Trip Reviews sub-menu and Review Tab, while travelers (users) can add reviews to the individual trips from the Review Tab in the frontend. Admin can later approve or unapprove the reviews. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also list all the reviews in tabs or trip content using the shortcode <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">- <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">[Wte_Trip_Review_List]<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews helps you get more trip bookings with social proof. It calculates the average ratings for a trip based on the total number of reviews. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews is SEO optimized. The reviews rich snippet is shown in search engines which increases Click Through Rate (CTR), and therefore, helps to improve search engine ranking. It also encourages your travelers to leave reviews and in turn increase conversion of your travel agency.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Screenshots<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-trip-reviews-global-setting.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43788\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-trip-reviews-global-setting.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1196\\\" height=\\\"2420\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-trip-reviews-tab-admin-review.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43789\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-trip-reviews-tab-admin-review.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1189\\\" height=\\\"1933\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-trip-reviews-tab-reviews.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43790\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/wp-travel-engine-trip-reviews-tab-reviews.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1177\\\" height=\\\"1277\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/08\\/review-tab-1.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2111\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/08\\/review-tab-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"780\\\" height=\\\"611\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Reviews is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows a tour operator or a travel agency to add authentic trip reviews onto their website.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/08\\/Trip-Review.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.1.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1750,\n                \"slug\": \"partial-payment\",\n                \"title\": \"Partial Payment\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-20 09:02:55\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:40:46\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1750\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Partial Payment is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a>. Partial Payment makes it easier for the travelers to book for a trip or tour package on an installment payment basis. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The tour operators and travel agencies can specify the partial payment rate of the trip in percentage or amount while creating the package. Later, travelers can book the package at a specified installment cost. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When using Partial Payment with WP Travel Engine, the travelers can view the Total Remaining Payment and Deposit Payable Amount on the checkout page. This results in better user experience and increases in sales or conversion.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Partial Payment can be applied to each trip individually.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour Operators and Agencies can choose whether to specify the Partial Payment rate in Percentage or in Amount. <\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Accept Partial Payment in Percentage:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> The partial payment amount of the trip price <\\/span><b>in percentage<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> to be paid while booking the trip. <\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Accept Partial Payment in Amount:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> \\u00a0The partial payment amount of the trip price <\\/span><b>in figures<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> to be paid while booking the trip.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h4>Screenshots<\\/h4>\\r\\nPartial Payment Global Settings<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Partial-Settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43460\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Partial-Settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1688\\\" height=\\\"810\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nPartial Payment Trip Settings<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43462\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Partial-trip-settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1282\\\" height=\\\"713\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nPartial Payment on Checkout Page<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43461\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/partial-checkout.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1569\\\" height=\\\"811\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Partial Payment is an extension for WP Travel Engine. Partial Payment makes it easier for the travelers to book for a trip or tour package in an installment payment basis.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Partial-Payment-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"19.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"49.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"69.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1757,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-search\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Search\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-20 08:10:21\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:42:41\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1757\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that provides a one-step trip search engine to search trips by Destination, Activities, Duration, and Budget on your travel website. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/trip-fixed-starting-dates\\/\\\"><b>Fixed Trip Starting Dates<\\/b><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> is another extension for WP Travel Engine that adds Fixed Starting Dates for a trip. If the add-on is added, then the trip can also be searched according to the Trip Starting Dates.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search indexes all the trip posts and adds destination, activity, duration, budget, and trip starting dates as search filters in a dropdown. <\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Destination<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - Users can search for trips by Destination such as Pokhara, Mustang, etc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Activities<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - Users can search for trips by Activities such as Paragliding, Rafting, etc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Duration<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - Users can search for trips by Duration such as 5 days, 10 days.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Budget<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - Users can search for trips by the Budget range. <\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Trip Starting Dates<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - Users can search for trips by Trip Starting Dates. <\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search extension also allows you to choose which filters (destination, activity, duration, budget) to exclude from the search.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search is a very good solution for tour operators and travel agencies to increase user experience and sales or conversion.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4><strong>Screenshots<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\nTrip Search Global Settings<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Trip-Search-Admin-Settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-43464 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/Trip-Search-Admin-Settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1339\\\" height=\\\"1099\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nTrip Search Bar on Home Page<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/search.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1758 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/search.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1161\\\" height=\\\"148\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nTrip Search Results Page<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Trip-Search-Result-\\u2013-Travel-Agency-Pro.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1759 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Trip-Search-Result-\\u2013-Travel-Agency-Pro.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1233\\\" height=\\\"1651\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Search is an extension for WP Travel Engine that provides a one-step trip search engine to search trips by Destination, Activities, Duration, and Budget on your travel website. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Trip-Search-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.6\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1744,\n                \"slug\": \"payfast-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayFast Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-20 08:07:19\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:44:07\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1744\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayFast Payment Gateway is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of South Africa\\u2019s popular merchant service, PayFast. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayFast booking system for trip booking by setting up PayFast Account with key details - Merchant Key and Merchant ID. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayFast Payment Gateway, they are redirected to your merchant account on PayFast where they are requested to login and make the payment. PayFast handles the payments and redirects the traveler back to your website. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which countries does PayFast support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayFast is a payment processing service for South Africa. It connects local and international buyers and sellers on a single platform with multiple ways to pay. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Payment from any country can be accepted, as long as you use ZAR as the currency. To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.payfast.co.za\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayFast Global Page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/01\\/Payfast-settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-29429 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/01\\/Payfast-settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"872\\\" height=\\\"827\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1747 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/PayFast-Engine-Payment-Methods.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1041\\\" height=\\\"396\\\" \\/>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayFast Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of South Africa\\u2019s popular merchant service, PayFast. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/PayFast.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"ZAR\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1055,\n                \"slug\": \"payu-biz-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayU Biz Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-19 08:55:50\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:44:48\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1055\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Payment Gateway is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of leading financial services in global growth markets, PayU. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayU Payment gateway for trip booking by setting up PayU Account with key details - Merchant Key and Merchant Salt. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayU Payment Gateway, the traveler is taken to PayU to make a secure payment. No SSL certificate is required on your site. After payment, the trip booking is confirmed and the traveler is redirected to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Payment Gateway incorporates payment methods like Credit Card, Debit Card, Internet Banking, and PayPal. The travelers can make card payments as well as direct payments via any of the associated banks. This results in increased conversion rates, improved customer experience and access to the global market.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1741\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Screenshot_2018-07-16-PayUbiz-300x283.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"563\\\" height=\\\"532\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1742\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/WP-Travel-Engine-Admin-Settings-\\u2039-wptravelengine-PayU-300x189.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"514\\\" height=\\\"324\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayU Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of leading financial services in global growth markets, PayU. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/PayU-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"INR\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 557,\n                \"slug\": \"stripe-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"Stripe Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-26 09:44:18\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:45:34\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=557\",\n                \"content\": \"This Stripe Payment Gateway extension allows you to accept credit cards directly on your website through <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stripe.com\\/\\\">Stripe.com<\\/a>\\u00a0account.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen using Stripe payment gateway with WP Travel Engine, the travelers enter their credit card details on the checkout page and never leave your site. This results in better user experience and increases in sales or conversion.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Which countries does Stripe support?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nStripe is currently available in many countries. It is also constantly expanding to more countries. \\u00a0To know if your country is supported, please visit the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stripe.com\\/global\\\">Stripe Global page<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Does Stripe require my site to have an SSL certificate?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nYes, you will need to use SSL certificate with Stripe. The pages that include a payment form should be prefixed with <i>https:\\/\\/<\\/i>. For more information, please visit <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stripe.com\\/docs\\/security\\\">Stripe Security page<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery link=\\\"file\\\" size=\\\"large\\\" columns=\\\"2\\\" ids=\\\"566,565,564\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This Stripe Payment Gateway extension allows you to accept credit cards directly on your website through Stripe.com account.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Stripe-Payment.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 8,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"wte\": {\n                \"supported_currencies\": [\n                    \"GBP\",\n                    \"USD\"\n                ]\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.2\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 146,\n                \"slug\": \"group-discount\",\n                \"title\": \"Group Discount\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-01-15 13:17:44\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:46:45\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=146\",\n                \"content\": \"Do you want to provide group discounts and increase sales?\\r\\n\\r\\nGroup Discount\\u00a0extension allows you to provide a group discount on the basis of the number of travelers booking a tour. In addition, it allows you to set a discount range(1-5, 5-10, 10-Unlimted) for adult, child, and infant groups separately.\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Giving a group discount is a great way to increase the conversation rate and the number of bookings. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a trip includes group discounts allowing a customer to book for multiple people, the customer can immediately book the trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4><strong>Screenshots<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\nGlobal Settings<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/gd-settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-41451\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/gd-settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1901\\\" height=\\\"730\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nTrip Settings<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/gd-trip-settings.gif\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-41483\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/gd-trip-settings.gif\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1269\\\" height=\\\"814\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nGroup Discount - Single Trip\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/gd-single-trip.gif\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-41491\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/gd-single-trip.gif\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"504\\\" height=\\\"814\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to give group discount to their customers.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/06\\/group-discount.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.0.3\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 79,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-fixed-starting-dates\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Fixed Starting Dates\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-01-10 11:38:32\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2021-02-23 12:49:04\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=79\",\n                \"content\": \"By default, all the trips can be booked throughout the year. Do you have trips with fixed departure dates and want them booked only on these days?\\r\\n\\r\\nTrip Fixed Starting Dates\\u00a0extension allows you to set specific dates when the trips can be booked. In addition, it allows you to set the number of available spots and recurring time.\\r\\n<h2>Features<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Trip Starting Dates<\\/strong>: You can add unlimited trip starting dates for every trip.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Space\\/Seat Available:<\\/strong> You can add a number of available seats for every trip starting dates.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Automatically Reduce Space\\/Seat:<\\/strong> After each trip booking, the number of available seats gets calculated automatically until the number of seats gets sold out.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Recurring Time<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Daily \\u2013 You can set daily recurring trips, starting from a given date, till recursion time limit.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Weekly \\u2013\\u00a0You can set weekly recurring trips on selected weekdays, starting from a given date, till recursion time limit.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Monthly \\u2013\\u00a0You can set monthly recurring trips on selected months, starting from a given date, till recursion time limit.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Yearly \\u2013 You can set yearly recurring trips, starting from a given date, till recursion time limit.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Recursion Limit: <\\/strong>You can set the number of times a particular date is recurred, including the start date.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Short Codes:<\\/strong> You can change the position where the fixed starting dates are displayed using the shortcodes.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>All Fixed Starting Dates:<\\/strong> You can display fixed starting dates from all the trips using the shortcode - [WTE_TRIPS_FIXED_STARTING_DATES]. Shortcode filters allow you to view trips by all available months and years.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h4>Screenshots<\\/h4>\\r\\nGlobal Settings<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/fsd-settings.gif\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-40980\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/fsd-settings.gif\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1891\\\" height=\\\"828\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nTrip Settings <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/fsd-trip-settings.gif\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-41000\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/fsd-trip-settings.gif\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1271\\\" height=\\\"828\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nTrip Fixed Starting Dates - Single Trip <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/fsd-trip-single.gif\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-41398\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/fsd-trip-single.gif\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1515\\\" height=\\\"828\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nAll Fixed Departure Dates<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/All-FSD.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-60286\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/12\\/All-FSD.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1235\\\" height=\\\"864\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to show trip fixed starting dates and number of space available for booking.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/08\\/Trip-Fixed-Starting-Dates.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 27,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.2.1\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        }\n    ],\n    \"request_speed\": 0.0277168750762939453125\n}', 'no');
